  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>인쇄 홈페이지 전문 기업,</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8bcd13ad-5c8f-47b1-850e-2421e9a43095\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5f63c043-e006-4cdc-8b9b-5068bca05d81\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>인쇄 전문 블로그,</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bb4fb7cc-ee2c-4484-8479-39f6c071a7d8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6ab8b9eb-69f4-4286-b1ab-5b37599e4c75\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>인쇄 자동 견적 시스템</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-71b77b3d-40f2-4ce2-a91f-5f65a79c62bb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223779723645/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2b55eb0c-faf1-47ed-ba42-bd40ed534e7a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:567px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223779723645/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-4101916d-9615-4780-8684-4e967e96a31e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-156e84ba-4ae8-4562-ac8a-0b0c2d8c4089\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-81bb8efa-d230-4ee9-ad8d-dc33e90d7d5d\" style=\"\">이런 회사라면 연락 주세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4a517379-6f78-4d94-bbed-54412ba82167\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-359d4892-16be-4c35-a2f0-7bab0af91df5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0b6e608f-8d03-40d1-987d-1afd988a31fd\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>□ 직원이 3인 이하인 작은 인쇄회사</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b3bc9530-8176-4ade-b680-04003e37d709\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ec25a0c9-5df5-415f-a74e-fa25365dd39b\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>□ 월 매출이 3,000만 원 미만인 소규모 인쇄소</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c7e241f5-9df9-4e0b-8afd-74777c596608\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0d41a385-6f4e-4ec7-b439-9530526c6a9d\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>□ 사이트가 없거나 있어도 관리를 하지 않고 있는 회사</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cbb4cfbf-560f-4616-b60a-7214ab8bb8bd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-923064ff-4b71-429d-b3ba-dd48f2bf32e6\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>□ 지금까지는 지인영업에만 의존한 회사</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-52482e75-eb13-49bb-8cbf-22951a75544f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-db4aa280-38e7-4b99-b585-15b1a428b504\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>□ 신규 사업이나 장비 투자 계획이 있으신 인쇄회사</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8a691521-c019-4e59-9ccf-825bc5a85d50\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-eff047f9-caf0-4488-a388-9a13fa5d9d09\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0c1ca002-93b6-444f-8bef-ceae94eed780\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-70d5bb27-b39f-453f-a79c-a9e522320727\" style=\"color:#555555;\">지금 이 블로그를 읽고 계신 분 중에 위 5가지 중 3가지 이상의 조건에 해당되신다면 지금 바로 전화나 톡톡을 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ac55b74c-9f2c-4e90-b444-ca114b9f518b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n<a class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223779723645/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bc527efa-8aa5-4bf6-8934-1f98629e81f7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223779723645#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4ee6b2ac-c8a8-4a00-bc60-438aaa2b9963\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223779723645/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-605a1e90-b51b-4dcf-ab26-c96b18e21ba5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223779723645/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-f0de627f-a75f-4e18-b833-82f9cc133b8e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bb649f29-e3f1-42d0-aa67-814dc082d038\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-eda4edc6-e5c3-4e13-9383-7bd3f25a6fcd\" style=\"\">사이트가 죽어가는 이유</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-48e56be3-e6ed-4143-a989-5893c6010be5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-136e4f64-77fc-4c75-aa9a-415342ed1a35\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-09fdbced-f9a0-41af-ad0d-7c85f5faa435\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄 사이트뿐 아니라 여러분의 사이트가 죽어가는 이유는 여러 가지가 있겠지만 대부분 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-816e4125-b878-4810-9086-83c4d00a2921\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>유지관리의 문제</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dde6c251-1b47-403f-a692-4086545f5241\" style=\"color:#555555;\">일 겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ec15e722-9a76-44f1-ad54-d4e827352140\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3ff24d76-d256-40da-9d7b-f80417ad14ed\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2cba1de0-e39e-441a-9813-912c4eca0508\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8159044b-74e2-4dd1-a00f-b0c56edfb643\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">초기에는 엄청나게 많은 비용을 들여 사이트를 개발했지만 지속적인 업데이트나 유지 보수에 많은 비용이 들고 또는 담당 직원의 교체나 개발 회사의 폐업으로 인해 갈 길을 잃어가는 경우가 허다합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4bfb09e5-3c2b-4d37-977b-e109d0c0fecb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-54c81f0e-f40c-4d10-95fb-acfff289427b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a78bf613-c1af-478a-85ba-9405a3688097\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5827493f-dd28-48d0-b08f-63cc7b99e803\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 문제를 단 한 번의 계약이나 개발로 해결할 수는 없습니다. 해결하는 방법은 지속적으로 관리를 해줄 수 있는 믿음 있는 회사와의 계약이나 또는 정식 직원을 채용하여 웹마스터 개념으로 관리를 하는 방법밖에 없습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-231aae64-1641-40de-9fbe-d5f49fe94e31\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2d302589-4983-4a39-8bbf-93a8e76df82e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9bb0b301-0895-45b3-9a17-f32bf9e1cb76\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cde4c143-ff9c-4bf3-95d7-d4e1aed4bdf8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 쉬운 일은 아닙니다. 직원 채용은 물론 수십 년을 넘게 계속적으로 관리해 줄 업체를 찾는 건 정말 어렵습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0bdb419c-1e23-41c9-8e7b-3096183d1753\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bb20a2bf-5d04-40c6-bd44-8b37404f96c8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e3ebff0f-5cb8-410b-b0fb-268aab9b2715\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-02234f15-8c3a-4f54-92fa-187dddfd3847\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 문제를 해결하기 위해 다음 사항을 체크하시고 계약하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-03aca7ac-528b-44b3-a54f-9f6511c9fc6d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-60c95b87-aaed-4154-9108-2e3a23826f37\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e458d127-8d87-44b7-afdb-0354c5479847\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8f56e130-cab5-4a7e-8484-eef9494b7fe6\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>□ 메뉴 하나 추가하는데 비용이 얼마일까요?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d187bf84-bd31-4025-88ae-13e27cfca784\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8dc3e814-535e-4ef5-a6cd-cac5d5e234d2\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>□ 배너나 포트폴리오를 추가하는데 비용이 드나요?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-541c2e9c-06d2-41e2-b84b-3f8599a0a8b4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-62bf0046-f7a7-4c56-a57d-debbf0ba8527\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>□ 서버 비용이나 기타 유지 보수 비용이 비쌀까요?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e704ca43-e157-4afb-ab8c-b4548f44aee1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e97664ff-f6b0-4dff-a129-962f449a69b5\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>□ 회사가 망하면 소스는 받을 수 있을까요?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-48e8ef3b-ba19-49bf-9913-686a25fcc46a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-653a0045-bb8e-44c4-895e-7fe19e4213fe\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>□ 월 유지 보수나 담당 PM이 계속 관리를 해주시는 걸까요?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2cbe5b74-725c-4e75-ab71-fa5e8b6541f7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0754772d-ee33-4775-9219-7e54c17aabb9\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fc1c8e2f-1682-492b-87f1-a532db445a7b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dc7b9ddf-2b25-4fe5-a56d-a512a57fa24c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 다음과 같은 연속성 문제를 해결하기 위해 고객과의 끊임없는 소통에 최선을 다합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f3e82623-f5c1-427b-ad09-81550df07d67\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9fb14475-64d3-49e1-b852-a7acc6d9f563\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-925282d9-4b15-4126-8817-477e5bb2a0f6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2b18e353-d430-4d4f-82f0-ea0c78936cc3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">개발 후에도 매월 담당 PM이 방문하여 사이트의 문제점이나 개선방안을 논의하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-872daa29-5dbf-4b50-8cfd-82fd05762c02\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-974b0d9e-61c8-408a-929d-18704a090cca\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ffc3feb3-f007-4c8b-847b-87d0e05f38e0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6eddc8cc-4135-4bd3-8a2a-57617ad151dd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또한 가장 문제가 되는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ce85a039-17e1-41ca-b487-be9bf16be98f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>콘텐츠 작업</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0acae43c-b04d-4bb4-b7af-fcb952119d9b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">을 합리적인 조건으로 대행해 드리고 있습니다. 여기서 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-24bc28bb-d667-45f5-b6f0-b197c197c28c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">콘텐츠라는 것은 회사에서 보유하고 있는 모든 디자인이나 기타 자료를 의미합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6dba64ed-1a79-4ecb-849c-1588465cd955\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-63dfc1da-f95b-475a-add1-ce17165354d0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1d8a37f4-f39d-48a8-85c8-94048aaa611c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5941497e-0c8f-41f7-8335-25d1f29df42b\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><u>*콘텐츠란 사이트를 구축하기 위한 디자인이나 설명 자료의 총칭을 말합니다. 인쇄회사라면 포트폴리오나 주문방법 등의 설명 등이 여기에 속한다고 보시면 됩니다.</u></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ded45493-5469-43af-bb1a-7ba17f323917\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2d85d638-4229-4120-976d-4a29177ae1bf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a309ab06-c511-4644-8c83-01470c0ca26a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-108dc453-d20a-478d-83d6-2dfe42225445\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제품 이미지나 기타 문구를 쉽게 변경할 수 있도록 최선을 다해 제공해 드리고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-71ee21e2-497e-46c4-9a6b-fe6e49347294\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223779723645/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_lin